title: DISCUSSING JEFF WITTEK VS DAVID DOBRIK — BFFs EP. 72
description:
We talk about Jeff Wittek’s recent comments on why he’s upset with David Dobrik, Mads Lewis breaking up with her boyfriend and refusing to come on the podcast, Addison Rae’s new movie deal and much more.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
